00:07:57.510 --> 00:08:00.690
So it puts you immediately
into the thought pattern

00:08:00.690 --> 00:08:03.150
of a detective-- cui bono?

00:08:03.150 --> 00:08:05.160
Who benefits?

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:09.630
Buy the person you are engaged
