00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:23.860
Why did this person
send me this message?

00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:26.600
Very important question.

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:29.230
Let's look at the news.

00:09:29.230 --> 00:09:32.530
