horrifying new development.

00:09:49.180 --> 00:09:52.240
And certainly, you're going
to find even more of that

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:55.060
the more you get to the
extremes and the less credible

00:09:55.060 --> 00:09:56.090
the source is.

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:02.920
Why did this person
send me the message?

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:12.040
The news organizations can alter
public opinion without lying--

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:14.540
