to you repeatedly?

00:10:59.509 --> 00:11:02.050
That's one of the first and most
valuable and important signs

00:11:02.050 --> 00:11:05.840
because propaganda
is repetition.

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:08.370
Propaganda is
repetition-- repetition,

00:11:08.370 --> 00:11:10.039
