research and analysis company

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:46.080
here in Seal Beach and
when they inactivated

00:16:46.080 --> 00:16:49.560
with the 15th tactical
up in upland California--

00:16:49.560 --> 00:16:52.020
both fine units.

00:16:52.020 --> 00:16:57.010
PSYOP deals with
foreign personnel,

00:16:57.010 --> 00:16:59.670
whether you're dealing
with enemy combatants

00:16:59.670 --> 00:17:02.940
or you're dealing with
civilians or enemy combatants.

00:17:02.940 --> 00:17:06.119
We have rained artillery
