00:17:23.824 --> 00:17:24.339
Abu Ghraib.

00:17:24.339 --> 00:17:27.174
So and they,
therefore, surrender,

00:17:27.174 --> 00:17:29.340
which means that they are
not fighting to the death,

00:17:29.340 --> 00:17:31.470
we're not having to fight
people to the death,

00:17:31.470 --> 00:17:33.280
and lives are saved.

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:36.630
Now, this is a weapon system,
classified as a weapon system.

00:17:36.630 --> 00:17:38.640
And we're prohibited
from using it on you,

00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:42.004
but the point is lives
were saved on both sides.

00:17:42.004 --> 00:17:44.170
And I think everybody can
get behind that, no matter

00:17:44.170 --> 00:17:48.030
where they stand on the
interventions in the Gulf.

00:17:48.030 --> 00:17:51.600
Another example might be
interfacing with civilians.

00:17:51.600 --> 00:17:54.570
Hey, folks, this is
