00:17:54.570 --> 00:17:56.910
Please don't drive here.

00:17:56.910 --> 00:17:58.230
Please don't walk here.

00:17:58.230 --> 00:17:59.700
Even if you're a
refugee, we really

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:03.270
hate picking you out
of our tank treads.

00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:04.590
Sorry, black humor.

00:18:04.590 --> 00:18:06.850
All right, that's
what PSYOP units do,

00:18:06.850 --> 00:18:09.480
and I was involved in that,
in the production of it--

00:18:09.480 --> 00:18:14.130
researching and profiling
target audiences when

00:18:14.130 --> 00:18:15.480
I was in the research company.

00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:20.580
Tactical PSYOP is a little
bit more boots on the ground,

00:18:20.580 --> 00:18:21.960
using loudspeakers.

00:18:21.960 --> 00:18:25.830
As an example, you wheel
up a loudspeaker up

00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:29.252
to some enemy unit, and you play
the sound of tanks going on.

00:18:29.252 --> 00:18:30.960
And they think, oh,
we're being attacked.

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:31.543
No you're not.

00:18:31.543 --> 00:18:33.630
It's a loudspeaker, fine.

00:18:33.630 --> 00:18:35.500
You do that two
times, three times,

00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:36.750
they start getting used to it.

00:18:36.750 --> 00:18:40.490
By the 30th time, it's
a real tank company.

00:18:40.490 --> 00:18:42.990
So yeah, there's a lot of wicked
supervillain stuff going on

00:18:42.990 --> 00:18:43.857
here.

00:18:43.857 --> 00:18:45.940
But the things that I would
like to tell you about

00:18:45.940 --> 00:18:49.290
are the things that I
saw in civilian world.

00:18:49.290 --> 00:18:52.710
I was on the set of a television
show-- no names, please.

00:18:52.710 --> 00:18:55.470
Here's the DP saying--

00:18:55.470 --> 00:18:58.150
I'm standing in, so I'm right
