the Coke in the other.

00:19:03.300 --> 00:19:05.160
We pan down from that
to the drink, then

00:19:05.160 --> 00:19:07.770
over here to our actor
sitting in the booth,

00:19:07.770 --> 00:19:10.680
and I get my $25,000, right?

00:19:10.680 --> 00:19:11.919
Now, a side fact--

