00:19:19.230 --> 00:19:20.230
It's a long story.

00:19:20.230 --> 00:19:21.930
But I mean, also,
look how simple

00:19:21.930 --> 00:19:25.890
it was for them to slip a
Drambuie and a Coca-Cola

00:19:25.890 --> 00:19:28.104
commercial right there
into your television show.

00:19:28.104 --> 00:19:29.520
And I can show you
that on Netflix

00:19:29.520 --> 00:19:31.186
right now when you
think you're watching

00:19:31.186 --> 00:19:33.090
